At an affordable price point of N25, Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita is creating positive impression in the marketplace. Among the consumers who volunteered their opinion on the brand was Joseph Uju, a Lagos based journalist. He noted that Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita is uniquely refreshing, affordable, great tasting and comes in a variant of his favourite fruit. “Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita comes in my preferred fruity variant of Red Berries and is ideal for frequent shots of great tasting refreshment throughout the day. It is very affordable and its 100ml size ensures that I can take several packs along with me to the office to ensure optimal value addition in terms of quality refreshment from my beverage,” he added. In the same vein, Michael bosun, who runs a thriving graphic design outfit in Ilupeju, praised Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita for being a healthier and affordable beverage option for refreshment from the range of products available on the shelf. “I have since taken to Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita because it resonates with my lifestyle and is a clear favourite for its natural fruity benefits as well as refreshing goodness. Its handy size means I can have it for refreshment during and after a hectic day’s schedule,” Eteng said. Speaking about the product and the positive feedback from consumers, Marketing Director of CHI Limited, Mr. Probal Bhattacharya said the response from consumers was a validation of the brand’s avowed commitment to being the leader in innovation and price strategy in the fruit beverage space. He added that at a price point of N25, Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita is the most affordable value for money offering for a healthy refreshment drink in the market.